name: pyepsg
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "0.3.1" %}

package:
    name: pyepsg
    version: {{ version }}

source:
    fn: pyepsg-{{ version }}.tar.gz
    url: https://github.com/rhattersley/pyepsg/archive/v{{ version }}.tar.gz
    sha256: e278656ad5fbe5ec97d08f690fa18b3d9149e842b4c6f383409aee5c5e8bf528

build:
    number: 0
    script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record record.txt

requirements:
    build:
        - python
    run:
        - python
        - requests

test:
    imports:
        - pyepsg

about:
    home: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/pyepsg
    license: LGPL
    summary: Easy access to the EPSG database via http://epsg.io/

extra:
    recipe-maintainers:
        - pelson
        - rhattersley
        - ocefpaf

about.summary: Easy access to the EPSG database via http://epsg.io/
